title: FormCraft 3.7.3 - Premium WordPress Form Builder
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org FormCraft WordPress Plugin is the most complete, flexible & customizable Drag & Drop Form Builder tool for WordPress on the market. FormCraft WordPress Plugin works on one standalone installation, or any one site on a WPMS installation. An add-on is required to use the plugin across all the sub-sites of a WordPress Multi-Site Installation. FormCraft WordPress Plugin Nulled has been designed and developed from the ground up with scalability and responsiveness at its core. No matter the device, FormCraft Nulled has a display resolution ready to take it on, whether it’s mobile, smartphone, tablet or even smartwatch your web forms will never have looked better.
